FBIS4-66010 "drweu103_a_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-103 Daily Report 27 May 1994 AUSTRIA Foreign Minister Mock in Hospital Foreign Minister Mock in Hospital AU2705122494 Vienna Oesterreich Eins Radio Network in German 0500 GMT 27 May AU2705122494 Vienna Oesterreich Eins Radio Network German BFN [Text] As we have already reported, Foreign Minister Alois Mock had to undergo hospital treatment yesterday. The official reason is a herniation of a vertebral disk. He is in an Innsbruck hospital. One of his closest aides told ORF Morgenjournal this morning that Mock is in good condition, considering the circumstances. Tests are going to be carried out, and the foreign minister will probably have to stay in hospital until next Wednesday [1 June].
